IMAPAccount antares@antares.me
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
AuthMechs LOGIN
User antares@antares.me 
PassCmd "pass Personal/Email/Gmail/mbsync"
#PassCmd "emacsclient -e '(password-store-get-field \"fastmail.com/myaccount@fastmail.com\" \"smtp\)'"
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore antares@antares.me-remote
Account antares@antares.me

MaildirStore antares@antares.me-local
Path ~/Maildir/antares@antares.me/
Inbox ~/Maildir/antares@antares.me/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel antares@antares.me
Far :antares@antares.me-remote:
Near :antares@antares.me-local:
#Patterns *
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "!Магазины*" "!Соцсети*" "!GitHub" "[Gmail]/Важное" "[Gmail]/Помеченные" "!Приоритетные" "!Прочие" "!Требуется ответ"
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
Create Both
SyncState *

